data.description: Beautiful Menomonee River Pkwy one of a kind custom Mid century home w/updated modern design. Built in 1956 this home has all of the elements of a Frank Lloyd Wright inspired design. Defined by its clean lines & undeniably timeless appeal. Large windows that invite the outside into the home, open concept LR  w/tall vaulted beamed ceilings. Beautifully updated KIT in upscale decor, vaulted ceilings, Shaker white cabinetry, custom tile work, double oven, pantry, granite counters, built in cook top/range & hood, breakfast island. FR w/fireplace, Stately large window w/transom. Updated full BA. DR w/custom built in buffet w/marble counters. This home has been modernly transformed while remaining aesthetically true to the midcentury era. 1.5 attached GA. HUGE & rare private yard w/new patio
